<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Making the Right Choice</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Most UK businesses benefit from using both tools. Perplexity handles research and fact-finding. ChatGPT manages creative and analytical tasks. This combination covers all bases effectively.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Consider your primary needs first. Research-heavy businesses lean towards Perplexity. Creative agencies prefer ChatGPT. Many successful UK companies integrate both into their workflows.</p>

